 Superior written and verbal communication skills 
 A demonstrated passion for technical recruiting and has customer obsession. 
 Attention to detail with exceptional analytical and process management skills with a data driven approach when it comes to reporting techniques 
 Skilled at partnering with hiring teams to build effective sourcing, assessment, and closing approaches with an ability to manage customer expectations 
 Strong technical sourcing skills with a track record of implementing innovative and effective strategies for sourcing passive candidates 
 Focus on results, ability to drive the recruiting process and provide responsive follow-up to both candidates and hiring teams 
 
